Text: An honor that belongs to only a few people. You'll bring the daybreak and grasp the light.

An honor only awarded to a small number of people. A proof of keeping pushing beyond one's limits.

Mountains crumble; Grimhorn shatters. A testament to the glory of defeating the source of Grimhorn Data.
Clouds disperse; the gleam fades. A testament to the glory of defeating the source of Bloom Data.
Twin dragons beheaded, an unending battle. A testament to the glory of defeating the sources of Grimhorn Data and Bloom Data in succession.

I shall become your wings and never leave.

"I saw a white horse, and Hell followed close behind."
From the chaotic, abyssal depths of hell, scattered demons claw their way out of mountains of corpses and seas of blood. They inherit the Death Lord's sovereign, earning the title of Sovereign.
Unwilling to be enslaved in the Sanctuary, choosing only to reign in hell.
"I'll break through this endless corridor and shatter the chains of fate!"
All wealth and ambition will submit to my desire.
Who says the laws set by the Supreme Heaven cannot be broken? I will turn that eternal daylight into a dreamless night.
